commit.message:
Merge pull request #8 from foobar8675/master

Updated Readme
ES6->ES5 compilation, refactored surface area, disabled CLI
Updated modules, renamed syndicate to engine
CLI: Added usage info when called without arguments
add test database env, avoid crash on invalid phantom js state, fix worker not clearing job, fix NEST_WORKERS env, fix spider checkStatus call

Merge pull request #6 from d-oliveros/revertMerge

Revert "Merge pull request #5 from d-oliveros/precompile"

Revert "Merge pull request #5 from d-oliveros/precompile"

This reverts commit 581c210c2fc6b90cbf253685038325559cff51dd, reversing
changes made to b60a6f9d197ea8790854fb51e4269c36fb6aa1d1.

Merge pull request #5 from d-oliveros/precompile

Added es6->es5 precompilation step and prepublish script
Added es6->es5 precompilation step and prepublish script
Expose items and jobs to be able to query them outside nest

Merge pull request #4 from d-oliveros/jobs-queue

Jobs queue
Refactored Actions to Jobs, engine to syndicate
Fixed worker loop, Added 'work' CLI command, added transitionDelay support, removed route dependency in Action.findOrCreate
remove prettyPrint from test/routes it crashes parsing a hole website

Merge pull request #3 from d-oliveros/spider-engine-abstraction

Nest workers
Added worker tests, all tests passing
Added spider tests, removed emitter prototype, removed events from spiders
Took routes out of spiders concern, refactored spider scrape
Abstracted spider and engine worker concerns
Fixed 'nest test' when providing route key

Merge pull request #2 from d-oliveros/global-cli

Added CLI, removed in-source routes, enhanced tests

Removed providers, added route key, added Testing 0 routes...

  0 passing (1ms) command
Created route prototype, refactored spider scraper

Merge pull request #1 from d-oliveros/refactor

Refactored codebase
Dynamic Spiders are no longer isolated in phantomJS's context
Modify symlink-setup.sh to deal with white spaces
Added route concurrency treshold, routeId to Operation schema, engine.stop method, tests
Added 'test', 'list' commands. Added log messages ENV
not sure what the changes are
Auto start the engine on domain init scripts
Added port option to mongo config
Added bin command and a symlink setup script
Changed reporter from nyan to spec
Added comments, increased logging level on engine run
added gitignore for jetbrains idea IDE series
Database models now initialize the mongo connection before exporting a mongoose model
Renamed bin to scripts, moved start script to index.js, better worker messages.
Removed query dependency on operation key generator
Deleted /data and /interface/server/scripts. Added github script on /bin/pwn-github
